title: Winterport Dragway celebrates racer appreciation day
text:
Winterport Dragway celebrates racer appreciation day By Staff | Oct 05, 2015 
Winterport — Racer appreciation day was celebrated on Sunday, Oct. 4 at Winterport Dragway, as regular bracket racing hit the strip as the season nears its conclusion. 
The individual results from Oct. 4 racing were: 
Super Pro/ Pro Final — 1, Mike Williams, Westbrook; and 2, Grady Tidd, Hodgdon. 
Super Pro Eliminator — 1, Grady Tidd, Hodgdon; and 2, Randy Therrien, Unity. Semifinalists: Paul Henckel, Old Orchard Beach; and Jennifer Fusco, Turner. 
Pro Eliminator — 1, Mike Williams, Westbrook; and 2, Jon Canty, West Gardiner. Semifinalist: Dwight Overlock, Owls Head. 
Street Eliminator — 1, Randy Herrick ,Stockton Springs; and 2, Bill Dammier, Deer Isle. Semifinalist: John Kaiser, Mapleton. 
Bikes and Sleds — 1, Tyler Wilkerson, Windham; and 2, Joanne Stiles ,Gorham. Semifinalist: Paul Keaten, Athens. 
Junior Dragster — 1, Danielle Fusco ,Turner; and 2, Jaylee Soucy, Monmouth. Semifinalists: Jonathan Condon, Chelsea; and Kerrigan Shorey, Lamoine.
